creator: Tapaw Groups
descriptionHtml:
TAPAW Driver – The app for Delivery Team Members!

Sign up now with your motorcycle, car, van, truck or lorry and earn as much as possible by working at your own flexible time as our logistic partner. Accept orders and deliver goods anytime anywhere which suit you best. Track your earnings easily in the apps and be your own boss today!

What Is Tapaw?

Tapaw is a smartphone app which provide competence platform that matches Drivers with users on-demand delivery in all regions of Malaysia. No matter what vehicles you’re driving, we welcome you to become our Logistic Partner that help us to matches with user’s delivery needs.

Ready to Get Started?

Step 1: Download and install the Tapaw Driver app

Step 2: Open the app, tap on ‘Sign Up’ and we’ll guide you step by step till you’re ready to hit the road and start earning your income.

Easy Income. Flexible Time. Get started Today.

Start earning by downloading the Tapaw Driver app to join us and we’ll guide you through each simple step to become Tapaw Partner Logistic today and get access to our support and training.
